  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation of PYTHON</title>

    <para>We will install PYTHON to enable extra functionality for GCC.
    It is not strictly required, but GCC can link to it to enable its
    new loop generation feature called Graphite.</para>

    <para os="a">Prepare PYTHON for compilation:</para>

<screen os="b"><userinput>./configure \
    --prefix=/cross-tools \
    --with-enable-pip=no </userinput></screen>

    <para os="c">Compile the package:</para>

<screen os="d"><userinput>make</userinput></screen>

    <para os="e">Install the package:</para>

<screen os="f"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

